text: Joaquín Humberto Vela González (born 11 February 1954) is a Mexican politician from the Party of the Democratic Revolution (formerly from the Labor Party). From 2006 to 2009 he served as Deputy of the LX Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing the State of Mexico. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:People from Aguascalientes City Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Party of the Democratic Revolution politicians Category:Labor Party (Mexico) politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians
